    "Proton VPN for Apple TV is available on all paid plans. You can check and manage your subscription on our website." : {
      "comment" : "Subtitle of the free upsell. Appears when a free user tries to log in to the tv app.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
